commit.message:
pretty-print.c (pp_integer_with_precision): Use HOST_LONG_LONG_FORMAT.

2008-05-11  Aaron W. LaFramboise  <aaronavay62@aaronwl.com>

	* pretty-print.c (pp_integer_with_precision): Use
	HOST_LONG_LONG_FORMAT.

From-SVN: r135171
